whose luck's run out.

461
00:34:59,363 --> 00:35:02,230
抱歉
GENEVlEVE: I'm sorry.

462
00:35:02,366 --> 00:35:04,891
我知道这很伤人
I know how much this hurts.

463
00:35:05,036 --> 00:35:06,663
看到她的所作所为
To see what she did.

464
00:35:06,804 --> 00:35:10,672
看清她的真正面目
To see who she really is.

465
00:35:11,943 --> 00:35:14,639
但你必须要知道
But you needed to know.

466
00:35:14,779 --> 00:35:18,408
你必须要看到
You needed to see it.

467
00:35:18,549 --> 00:35:23,248
现在你都知道了，你可以复仇了
And now that you have,
you can take your revenge.

468
00:35:23,387 --> 00:35:26,015
我们的复仇
Our revenge.

469
00:35:31,129 --> 00:35:33,859
来吧，喝吧
Please.
Go ahead.

470
00:35:33,998 --> 00:35:37,195
