in other ways.

487
00:38:47,491 --> 00:38:50,585
我不会再让你插匕首躺棺材了
No more daggered-in-a-box
for you.

488
00:38:52,863 --> 00:38:55,889
相信我，妹妹，你会怀念匕首的感觉的
Trust me, sister. You'll long
for what the dagger offered.

489
00:38:56,033 --> 00:39:00,060
这个，就没那么仁慈了
This will be far less merciful.

490
00:39:00,204 --> 00:39:04,300
要如何确切描述这把刀的用途呢？
How to describe exactly
what this blade does?

491
00:39:04,442 --> 00:39:06,467
你用不着这么做，尼克
You don't have to do this, Nik.

492
00:39:06,610 --> 00:39:11,206
当它插入你的心脏后
你将无法动弹
After I plunge this into your heart,
you will be immobilized,

493
00:39:11,349 --> 00:39:16,753
处在一种撕心裂肺的无比痛苦之中
imprisoned in a state of raw,
inescapable anguish.

494
00:39:16,887 --> 00:39:18,912
时间将毫无意义
Time loses all meaning.

495
00:39:19,056 --> 00:39:22,082
如同人间炼狱
因为你的背叛
It's not unlike a living hell,
which I find rather fitting

496
00:39:22,226 --> 00:39:23,557
我觉得这样处罚再适合不过了
given your treachery.

497
00:39:23,694 --> 00:39:28,097
那就动手吧
如果这就是你想要的
Then, do it.
If that's what you really want.

498
00:39:29,367 --> 00:39:32,165
我们跳过了你祈求饶恕的那段吗？
Are we skipping the part
where you beg for mercy?

499
00:39:32,303 --> 00:39:34,601
祈求我原谅？
For forgiveness?

500
00:39:34,739 --> 00:39:39,039
因为我本来真的很期待呢
Because I was really
looking forward to that.

501
00:39:41,212 --> 00:39:44,045
不必了
I'll pass.

502
00:39:44,181 --> 00:39:47,639
我很清楚这对我不会有什么好处
I know better than to think
it would do me any good.

503
00:39:49,954 --> 00:39:54,152
那就这样了吗？
你放弃抵抗了
That's it, then?
You concede.

504
00:39:55,459 --> 00:39:59,327
如同一头待宰的羔羊
Like a lamb to the slaughter.

505
00:39:59,463 --> 00:40:02,955
你觉得父亲会怎么想你？
What would your father
think of you, now?

506
00:40:39,103 --> 00:40:41,469
正是我想见的人
Just the man I wanted to see.

507
00:40:43,207 --> 00:40:44,936
看着你死，蕾贝卡的惩罚
Rebekah's punishment
won't be complete

508
00:40:45,075 --> 00:40:46,804
才算完整呢
until she watches you die.

509
00:40:46,944 --> 00:40:49,538
尼克，召唤麦可是我的主意
Nik, it was my idea
to summon Mikael.

510
00:40:51,215 --> 00:40:53,308
如果你要伤害谁，那一定就是我
If you're gonna hurt anyone,
it should be me.

511
00:40:53,451 --> 00:40:56,147
对你的爱人真是忠贞啊
Such loyalty to your beloved.

512
00:41:02,092 --> 00:41:03,252
你知道…
You know...

513
00:41:04,829 --> 00:41:07,627
如果你给过我哪怕是一丁点的忠诚
If you had offered me
even a fraction of the same,

514
00:41:07,765 --> 00:41:09,232
我也就不必这么做了
I wouldn't have to do this.

515
00:41:27,551 --> 00:41:28,540
走吧
Go.

516
00:41:31,422 --> 00:41:34,118
你们俩尽快逃走吧，越远越好
Both of you,
run as far and as fast as you can.

517
00:41:34,258 --> 00:41:35,589
跑啊！
Run!

518
00:41:49,473 --> 00:41:52,806
片名：创始吸血鬼（第一季）

